data.description: Sellers will consider interest rate buy down with acceptable offer. Enjoy the best of both worlds in this exquisite custom-built home nestled on a sprawling 7-acre estate. Located less than a 45-minute drive from Downtown Greenville, Anderson, and even closer to the vibrant Clemson University, this property offers a harmonious blend of convenience and tranquility. With the added assurance of a recent roof and HVAC system, you can relish a peace of mind that complements the unparalleled beauty of this property. The moment you step inside, you'll be captivated by the breathtaking mountain views that grace each window of this immaculate residence. With both attached and detached garage spaces, your vehicles and hobbies will find their perfect home here. Indulge in the well-thought-out design of this home, where rooms are thoughtfully separated to maintain an open and inviting ambiance while providing just enough sound isolation. Ascend to the upper level, where you'll discover a newly renovated master suite that provides a private sanctuary. This retreat boasts a spacious walk-in closet, an en-suite bath with a soaking tub, a separate shower, and individual vanities. You will enjoy your very own balcony, offering an ideal space to start or end your day, with the mountains as your backdrop. On the main level, two additional bedrooms await, paired with a full bath, making it easy to accommodate guests. The central kitchen seamlessly connects to the dining and breakfast areas, creating a functional and inviting space. Abundant cabinets, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances cater to the everyday cook. Take in the beautiful views and host an outside dinner party from a screened in porch off the kitchen and breakfast area. The main floor is completed by a grand living space featuring high beamed ceilings. It is ready to host multiple seating arrangements, whether you want to enjoy a favorite movie or cozy up by the gas log fireplace. The lower level offers incredible flexibility, making it suitable for use as an in-law suite, an office, or as ample storage space. There is a large space that can be used as a living room or movie area. An attached full bath and laundry ensures easy convenience. Step out onto the lower-level patio, complete with water and a 220V connection, making it ideal for a variety of outdoor activities. For your peace of mind, the property features a water filtration system to ensure a pure water supply, along with a sump pump for added preventative care, given its beautiful mountain location. This exceptional home offers the best in luxury living, combining stunning mountain vistas with the convenience of proximity to key destinations. Don't miss your chance to call this property your own!
